sources.description:
The Night Visitor 2: HEATHER'S STORY runs parallel to the original Night Visitor, telling the story of Heather, a special young girl, who must protect her family and the planet from the same other-earthly being. The sequel delves deeper into the mysteries that plagued the Stevens family and their son Ricky with the help of psychic and medium Daniel.  Stars Michael Biehn (Aliens) and Brianne Davis (Six)
2016.  Stars: Michael Biehn, Caitlin Carmichael, Jennifer Blanc-Biehn
